Project Summary
The proposed project e-IRGSP5 is intended to provide support to the e-Infrastructure Reflection Group (e-IRG). The support activities include:
ï	operation of the secretariat, e.g. organisation of events and provision of secretarial support to the e-IRG Chair and Executive Board;
ï	provision of editorial support during the preparation of policy documents, input to the Commission and support e-IRG working groups and task forces;
ï	liaison with e-IRGís various stakeholders and maintain e-IRGís social media channels
ï	communication of e-IRGís output;
ï	operation of the external and internal e-IRG web presence;
ï	collection and aggregation of policy information to enable assessment of e-infrastructures.
